message: Lauri and Brown were arrested Jan. 19 after a 38-year-old woman reported to police that she’d been held against her will and victimized.

data.description: Two Lawrence men charged in a human trafficking, rape and kidnapping case are trying to work out plea deals with prosecutors, their attorneys said in court Tuesday. data.title: Lawrence men seek plea deals in human trafficking, kidnapping case
